{{Maya civilization}}
'''Tamchen''' is an ancient [[Maya city]], located in the [[Yucatán Peninsula]], [[Mexico]]. It was discovered in August 2014, along with [[Lagunita]], by Ivan Sprajc, associate professor at the Research Center of the [[Slovenian Academy of Sciences and Arts]], and his team, after they reviewed aerial photographs of the area.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/08/22/mexico-mayan-cities-found_n_5700527.html|title= Ancient Mayan Cities Found In Mexican Jungle|date=August 22, 2014|accessdate=August 22, 2014|work=[[The Huffington Post]]}}</ref>

